# Cloudflare Pages routing rules (served from dist root)

# Serve the real Tribute page for the bare clean URL. This is a 200 (internal
# rewrite) whose destination is a plain static file with NO redirect on it, so
# it terminates immediately — no loop, and it defeats any directory-index or
# 404-fallback quirk that was serving Reception for /tribute/tk.
/tribute/tk     /tribute/tk/index.html    200

# Aliases -> clean tribute URL.
/tk-tribute.html    /tribute/tk    301
/tribute-tk         /tribute/tk    301
